    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. This example remains mechanically robust, having undergone documented preventive maintenance on the cooling system and rod bearings. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from a subframe inspection and firm bushings. Finished in a classic colorway, the car exhibits a clean interior and strong compression, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience for the discerning driver.",
