    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that has been treated with care. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the driver-side door handle\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin remains a quiet and comfortable sanctuary; the seats show only light bolstering wear typical of its age, and the interior is entirely smoke-free and pet-free. All electronic features, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has received regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the brakes were serviced just six months ago. The engine idles quietly and provides smooth, responsive power on the highway, while the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. Included are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service records to provide the next owner with total peace of mind.",
